This package implements the application logic.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientOperations
    Provides the means for the insert and delete client operations to be done.
    OrderOperations
    Provides the means for place order and erase orders and order item operations to be made
    ProductOperations
    Provides the means for insert, delete and update stock operations to be performed on products.
    Validator
    Used to validate the operations that can be done using this application.
